as', 'Formal Education', 'Procedures', 'Dates', 'Links ', 'Council of Higher Education', 'Dokuz Eylül University', 'DEU Student Affairs Office', 'DEU International Affairs Office', 'DEU Course Catalog Information Package', 'DEU Library', 'Contact Us', 'Master of Music (MMus)', 'MASTER of MUSIC (MMus)', 'Profile of theProgram', 'The Second Cycle Program of Opera Department is primarily intended for students who hold a Bachelor’s degree in Opera and whose aim is to be specialized in field and make a academic career or make a progress as a performer. Students of this program during the first two semesters besides taking performance lessons such as Voice Training, Acting, Opera and Song Literature, they also improve their substructure knowledge of music by taking theoretical courses such as Opera History and Voice Anatomy and Physiology. The education process ends up with a thesis that would be completed in two semesters and a final recital. The students may use the music library, music studio and practice rooms of conservatory.', 'Admission Requirement(s)', 'Source of Students for Admission', 'Number of Students', 'Beachlor’s DegreeDiploma', 'Transcript', 'C1 grade for Turkish language', 'Graduates of Conservatory (opera) can apply to this program.', '4+1', 'Portfolio', 'Interview', 'Live Audition*', 'Click', 'here', 'for more details about cource structure with credits, graduation requirements etc.', '** Live Audition Requirements: 1 French melody,1 German lied, 1 song (in any language). Songs are to be chosen at least from two different periods of music.1 Mozart aria,1 Baroque aria, 1 aria (from any period). All compositions must be performed in memory and sung in original language.One of the arias should be sung with its recitativo.', 'DEÜ Social Media', 'Address', 'DOKUZ EYLÜL ÜNİVERSİTESİ', 'GÜZEL SANATLAR ENSTİTÜSÜ', 'DEÜ TINAZTEPE YERLEŞKESİ', 'ADATEPE MAH. DOĞUŞ CAD. NO:209', '35390 BUCA – İZMİR/TURKEY', 'Contact', 'Tel: +90 (232) (', 'Administrative Assist.', 